  "root_text": {
    "an5.230:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5.230 ",
    "an5.230:0.2": "23. Dīghacārikavagga ",
    "an5.230:0.3": "Dutiyakaṇhasappasutta ",
    "an5.230:1.1": "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā kaṇhasappe. ",
    "an5.230:1.2": "Katame pañca? ",
    "an5.230:1.3": "Kodhano, upanāhī, ghoraviso, dujjivho, mittadubbhī. ",
    "an5.230:1.4": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā kaṇhasappe. ",
    "an5.230:2.1": "Evamevaṁ kho, bhikkhave, pañcime ādīnavā mātugāme. ",
    "an5.230:2.2": "Katame pañca? ",
    "an5.230:2.3": "Kodhano, upanāhī, ghoraviso, dujjivho, mittadubbhī. ",
    "an5.230:2.4": "Tatridaṁ, bhikkhave, mātugāmassa ghoravisatā—",
    "an5.230:2.5": "yebhuyyena, bhikkhave, mātugāmo tibbarāgo. ",
    "an5.230:2.6": "Tatridaṁ, bhikkhave, mātugāmassa dujjivhatā—",
    "an5.230:2.7": "yebhuyyena, bhikkhave, mātugāmo pisuṇavāco. ",
    "an5.230:2.8": "Tatridaṁ, bhikkhave, mātugāmassa mittadubbhitā—",
    "an5.230:2.9": "yebhuyyena, bhikkhave, mātugāmo aticārinī. ",
    "an5.230:2.10": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā mātugāme”ti. ",
    "an5.230:2.11": "Dasamaṁ. ",
    "an5.230:2.12": "Dīghacārikavaggo tatiyo. ",
    "an5.230:3.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "an5.230:3.1": "Dve dīghacārikā vuttā, ",
    "an5.230:3.2": "atinivāsamaccharī; ",
    "an5.230:3.3": "Dve ca kulūpakā bhogā, ",
    "an5.230:3.4": "bhattaṁ sappāpare duveti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an5.230:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 5.230 ",
    "an5.230:0.2": "23. Long Wandering ",
    "an5.230:0.3": "Black Snakes (2nd) ",
    "an5.230:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of a black snake. ",
    "an5.230:1.2": "What five? ",
    "an5.230:1.3": "It’s irritable, acrimonious, venomous, fork-tongued, and treacherous. ",
    "an5.230:1.4": "These are the five dangers of a black snake. ",
    "an5.230:2.1": "In the same way there are five drawbacks of a lady. ",
    "an5.230:2.2": "What five? ",
    "an5.230:2.3": "She’s irritable, acrimonious, venomous, fork-tongued, and treacherous. ",
    "an5.230:2.4": "This is a lady’s venom: ",
    "an5.230:2.5": "usually she’s very lustful. ",
    "an5.230:2.6": "This is a lady’s forked tongue: ",
    "an5.230:2.7": "usually she speaks divisively. ",
    "an5.230:2.8": "This is a lady’s treachery: ",
    "an5.230:2.9": "usually she’s an adulteress. ",
    "an5.230:2.10": "These are the five drawbacks of a lady.” ",
